\lim\limits_{x\to3}\frac{4x(x-3)}{|x-3|}
x \gt 3
x \lt 3
|x-3|
3-x
\lim_{x \to 3^+}\frac{4x(x-3)}{|x-3|}=\lim_{x \to 3^+}\frac{4x(x-3)}{x-3}=\lim_{x \to 3^+}4x=12
\lim_{x \to 3^-}\frac{4x(x-3)}{|x-3|}=\lim_{x \to 3^-}\frac{4x(x-3)}{3-x}=\lim_{x \to 3^-}-4x=-12
 r = \lim\limits_{x\to3+0}\frac{4x(x-3)}{|x-3|} = \lim\limits_{x\to3+0}\frac{4x(x-3)}{x-3} = 12 
 l = \lim\limits_{x\to3-0}\frac{4x(x-3)}{|x-3|} = \lim\limits_{x\to3-0}\frac{4x(x-3)}{-(x-3)} = -12 
r=l
